# Frontend Component Reference

> Mapping every component to its origin in [sss-dashboard-v2.jsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx) — the monolithic prototype the app was refactored from.

---

## Architecture Overview

```
sss-dashboard-v2.jsx (single-file prototype, 1441 lines)
       │
       ▼
Next.js App (app/ + components/)
  ├── app/layout.tsx          ← Root shell (server component)
  │     └── ClientLayout      ← All client-side chrome
  │           ├── Sidebar     ← Navigation drawer
  │           └── TopBar      ← Header bar
  └── app/<route>/page.tsx    ← Server component per page
        └── components/views/<Name>View.tsx   ← Client page body
```

**Key architectural shift**: The prototype used client-side `useState("page")` to switch pages. The Next.js app uses the **file-system router** — each URL maps to a real page, enabling server rendering and proper back/forward navigation.

---

## 1. [app/layout.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/app/layout.tsx) — Root Layout (Server Component)

**Source in v2**: Lines 1289–1438 — the top-level `<App>` return JSX (`<html>`, `<body>`, `<Fonts>`, `<AmbientBg>`, the `<motion.aside>` sidebar and `<motion.header>` topbar all lived inline in [App()](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx#1270-1441)).

| Responsibility | Detail |
|---|---|
| Sets `<html>` + `<body>` | Wraps everything with proper HTML skeleton |
| Imports [globals.css](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/app/globals.css) | CSS custom properties (`--bg`, `--accent`, etc.) that were inline `<style>` in v2 |
| Renders `<ClientLayout>` | Delegates all interactive chrome to the client boundary |
| Sets page `<title>` + meta | Via Next.js `Metadata` export — didn't exist in v2 |

---

## 2. [components/ClientLayout.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/ClientLayout.tsx) — Client Chrome Shell

**Source in v2**: The outer `div` + sidebar + topbar + `<main>` from [App()](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx#1270-1441) (lines 1292–1436).

| Responsibility | Detail |
|---|---|
| `sidebarOpen` state | **New** — not in v2. Enables mobile drawer toggle |
| `isMobile` via `matchMedia` | **New** — v2 had no responsive behaviour |
| Renders `<Sidebar>` | Passes `open` + `onClose` props (mobile-aware) |
| Renders `<TopBar>` | Passes `onMenuClick` for hamburger |
| Mobile backdrop overlay | **New** — `AnimatePresence` fade on `position: fixed` div |
| `<main>` page transitions | Same `AnimatePresence` + `motion.div` blur/y transition as v2 (line 1426–1434), but now keyed by `pathname` (from `usePathname`) instead of `page` state |
| `clamp()` padding | **New** — fluid mobile padding |

