## 6. `components/views/` — Page Bodies (Client Components)

In v2 these were all top-level function components inside the same file. In the Next.js app each is a separate `"use client"` file in `components/views/`.

| View file | v2 component | Route | Source lines |
|---|---|---|---|
| [DashboardView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/views/DashboardView.tsx) | [DashboardPage](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx#381-578) | `/` | L384–577 |
| [HoldersView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/views/HoldersView.tsx) | [HoldersPage](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx#579-648) | `/holders` | L582–647 |
| [ComplianceView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/views/ComplianceView.tsx) | [CompliancePage](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx#649-858) | `/compliance` | L652–857 |
| [AuditLogView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/views/AuditLogView.tsx) | [AuditPage](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx#859-942) | `/audit-log` | L862–941 |
| [WebhooksView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/views/WebhooksView.tsx) | [WebhooksPage](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx#943-1075) | `/webhooks` | L946–1074 |
| [OracleView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/views/OracleView.tsx) | [OraclePage](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx#1076-1257) | `/oracle` | L1079–1256 |

### Each view's internal responsibilities

#### [DashboardView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/views/DashboardView.tsx)
- `mintAmt`, `showKey`, `loading`, `txBanner` state
- Stat grid (4 × [StatCard](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx#231-257) with [CountUp](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/Primitives.tsx#113-134) values)
- Animated TX confirmation banner (`AnimatePresence`)
- Mint form (recipient, amount, keypair with show/hide + [KeypairWarning](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/Primitives.tsx#365-381))
- Burn form
- Recent Activity table (last 6 `MOCK_AUDIT` events)

#### [HoldersView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/views/HoldersView.tsx)
- `minAmt` filter state
- Total holders [CountUp](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/Primitives.tsx#113-134) hero stat
- Leaderboard table with share % bar animation
- [CopyBtn](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx#268-284) + Solscan link per holder row

#### [ComplianceView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/views/ComplianceView.tsx)
- `tab` state (`blacklist` | `check` | `seize`)
- `addModal`, `removeModal`, `seizeModal`, `seizeText` state
- Tab bar with `AnimatePresence mode="wait"` panel transitions
- **Blacklist tab**: list of frozen accounts, Add/Remove with modals
- **Check Address tab**: address lookup → clean/blacklisted result card
- **Seize tab**: confirm-word gate (`SEIZE` typed input) before executing

#### [AuditLogView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/views/AuditLogView.tsx)
- `actionFilter`, `actorFilter` state
- Filter bar (action dropdown + actor text input + animated Clear button)
- Events table with [ActionBadge](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/Primitives.tsx#286-289), [TxLink](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx#258-267), timestamps
- [Pagination](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/Primitives.tsx#384-410) bar

#### [WebhooksView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/views/WebhooksView.tsx)
- [hooks](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx#943-1075), `createModal`, `deleteModal`, `expanded` state
- Per-webhook toggle switch (animated thumb), expand-to-edit accordion
- Register + Delete modals
- Payload reference card (events + HMAC header format)

#### [OracleView.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/views/OracleView.tsx)
- `tab` state (`feeds` | `config` | `simulator`)
- **Feeds tab**: price feed cards + Register Feed form
- **Config tab**: fetch oracle config + Initialize Config form
- **Simulator tab**: Mint Quote + Redeem Quote calculators (pure maths, no RPC)

