## 7. `app/<route>/page.tsx` — Thin Server Page Wrappers

Each route folder contains a single [page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/app/page.tsx) that is a **React Server Component** — it simply imports and returns the corresponding View. This is how Next.js knows which view to render per URL.

```
app/page.tsx           →  <DashboardView />
app/holders/page.tsx   →  <HoldersView />
app/compliance/…       →  <ComplianceView />
app/audit-log/…        →  <AuditLogView />
app/webhooks/…         →  <WebhooksView />
app/oracle/…           →  <OracleView />
```

