## Key Differences Summary: v2 → Current App

| Concern | [sss-dashboard-v2.jsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx) (prototype) | Next.js App |
|---|---|---|
| Routing | `useState("page")` + `PAGES[page]` | File-system router (`app/`) |
| Server rendering | None (entirely client) | Server components at page level |
| Responsiveness | None | Mobile drawer + `matchMedia` |
| Global CSS | Inline `<style>` tag | [app/globals.css](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/app/globals.css) |
| TypeScript | No ([.jsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx)) | Yes ([.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/app/page.tsx)) — strict prop types |
| Component splitting | Single 1441-line file | Shared [Primitives.tsx](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/components/Primitives.tsx) + separate View files |
| Active route | `page === item.id` | `pathname.startsWith(href)` |
| Navigation | [goTo(id)](file:///c:/Users/sysadmin/Documents/projects/solana-stablecoin-standard/frontend/sss-dashboard-v2.jsx#1277-1278) (state mutation) | `<Link href>` (Next.js router) |
| `type: "spring"` | Inferred as `string` | `as const` → literal `"spring"` |
